# Frontend Next.js Rules

- App Router under `frontend/app/`; dashboard routes in `app/(dashboard)/`
- API calls go through `frontend/lib/api.ts` — do not scatter fetch logic
- Use Lucide icons and Tailwind zinc/indigo palette
- Client components need `"use client"` directive
- Match score badges: indigo >60%, amber 30–60%, red <30%
- Kanban uses @dnd-kit; always provide status dropdown as drag alternative
